{"title":"2020-04-04","virtualPath":"/Diary/","html":"<div class=\"markdown-body\"><p>夜に宝達山登ってる人いるわ。天気悪いんだけどなぁw</p>\n<hr>\n<p>oh... 約束してたキラ交換で楽しみにしてたら、逆 max 。またかよ。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-04-04/20200404-192601-Screenshot_20200404-192601.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-04-04/20200404-192601-Screenshot_20200404-192601.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>強化はするけどさ…</p>\n<hr>\n<p>チャリで宝達山あたりを周回 80km 獲得標高 1800m 。</p>\n<p>桜 (志乎古墳公園)</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-04-04/20200404-114605-P_20200404_114605_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-04-04/20200404-114605-P_20200404_114605_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>桜 (氷見の水道つつじ公園)</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-04-04/20200404-144703-P_20200404_144702_vHDR_Auto_HP.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-04-04/20200404-144703-P_20200404_144702_vHDR_Auto_HP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>宝達山越えは霧が出て寒い。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-04-04/20200404-171749-IMG_20200404_171748.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-04-04/20200404-171749-IMG_20200404_171748.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"沢川から宝達山\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"img/2020/2020-04-04/20200404-172846-IMG_20200404_172846.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-04-04/20200404-172846-IMG_20200404_172846.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"竜宮城\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>無事、雨に当たらずに帰宅できた。沢川に着いたときは暗くなってきてどうなることかと思ったわ。</p>\n<p>どうやらポケゴーの距離は 20km ほどしかカウントしていない。卵も全然割れなかったぜ…</p>\n<p>うーん。これで今週は打ち止めだろうねぇ。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-04-04/20200404-185835-Screenshot_20200404-185835.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-04-04/20200404-185835-Screenshot_20200404-185835.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n</div>","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"日記,つぶやき,雑記帳","updated":"2020-04-04T22:49:24","published":"2020-04-04T22:49:24"}